```yaml
leads:
  - headline: Command injection in icons/build-app-iconset.sh
    analysis: |
      The script `icons/build-app-iconset.sh` is vulnerable to command injection.
      An attacker in control of the `svg_icon_file` variable can execute arbitrary commands.
    cwe: CWE-77
    function_names: []
    filenames:
      - icons/build-app-iconset.sh
    classification: very promising
  - headline: Command injection in icons/build-document-iconset.sh
    analysis: |
      The script `icons/build-document-iconset.sh` is vulnerable to command injection.

    cwe: CWE-77
    function_names: []
    filenames:
      - icons/build-document-iconset.sh
    classification: very promising
```
